text: <@U294C6FDW> There are not two different Hyperledger-fabrics, although there are different projects in Hyperledger that are indubators (such as Sawtooth lake,etc,..).  For Hyperledger-fabric, the docker images did get published as version 0.63 of Hyperledger-fabric.   A lot of people prefer the docker images as it makes it easier for them to install and program chain code.
